Name: TV Kid
About the game: TV Kid is an addicting roguelike clicker game with endless possibilities for item combinations! Click through channel after channel and try to defeat television itself! List of Features: Every single run is completely randomized and different! 100+ items to find and collect! 3+ characters to unlock and play as! 25+ monsters to find and defeat! Includes a waifu body pillow!
